summary: Georgia's starting quarterback, Carson Beck, sustained a shoulder injury during the SEC Championship Game against Texas. After suffering the injury, backup quarterback Gunner Stockton took over and led the team to an overtime victory. Beck initially left the game after injuring his hand, but he returned to hand off the football on the final play of the game. The Bulldogs are now awaiting the results of an MRI to determine the extent of Beck's injury. The injury has cast a shadow over Georgia's victory as they prepare for the College Football Playoff semifinals.

name: Pearl Harbor day
summary: Today marks the 83rd anniversary of the attack on Pearl Harbor, a pivotal moment in American history that led to the country's entry into World War II. To honor and remember those who made the ultimate sacrifice, various organizations and government officials have issued statements and proclamations. Governor Gavin Newsom of California has declared Pearl Harbor Remembrance Day 2024, while Pacific Command held a ceremony to pass on the legacy to young service members. The Department of Defense and news outlets such as Hawaii News Now and WDSU New Orleans have all highlighted the importance of remembering this day. Governor Ron DeSantis of Florida has ordered flags to be flown at half-staff, while USA TODAY and LiveNOW from FOX shared photos and stories from the attack. EL PAÍS USA provided a timeline of events leading up to the fateful day, and the state of North Carolina has also lowered its flags in honor of National Pearl Harbor Remembrance Day.

name: Man City
summary: In a crucial Premier League clash, Liverpool emerged victorious over defending champions Manchester City with a 2-0 win, extending their lead to nine points. Despite City's recent title success, Pep Guardiola acknowledged that the season has been challenging for them, describing it as a "season to suffer." Liverpool's dominance was evident in the match, as they eased past City to solidify their position at the top of the league. The 11-point gap between the two teams highlights Liverpool's current strength. While Manchester City faced a setback in their Club World Cup ambitions, they managed to salvage a point against Crystal Palace despite playing with 10 men. Liverpool's triumph and City's struggles have amplified the intensity of the Premier League title race, with Liverpool looking to maintain their lead and City aiming to turn around their season.

summary: Mark Withers, the actor known for his roles in the popular television series "Dynasty" and "Stranger Things," has passed away at the age of 77. Withers' notable role as Jason Colby on Dynasty spanned three seasons, while he portrayed Hawkins' Mayor Kline in Stranger Things. Withers' career in television and film spanned several decades, and his contributions will be fondly remembered by fans and colleagues alike.

summary: Clemson upset No. 4 Kentucky in their SEC/ACC Challenge matchup, marking the first loss for the Wildcats under new coach Mark Pope. The game was a close battle, with Kentucky trailing by 15 points at halftime but eventually pulling off a rally. However, Clemson ultimately prevailed with a 70-66 score, led by Ian Schieffelin's impressive performance. In a separate game, Kentucky faced Gonzaga in a top-10 battle and pulled off an epic comeback in the second half to win in overtime. This victory showcased the team's resilience and their coach's ability to lead them to victory.

name: Cam Skattebo
summary: Cam Skattebo, an Arizona State University football running back, has emerged as a key player in the team's success. After overcoming early setbacks, Skattebo has powered the Sun Devils to a Big 12 title and into College Football Playoff contention. His mother, Becky Skattebo, has been instrumental in his upbringing and shares her perspective on raising her son. Despite not receiving an award nomination, Skattebo remains confident in his abilities, claiming to be the "best running back in the country." His fiery speeches and aggressive running style have captivated fans and media outlets. Skattebo's impressive performance has even led to predictions of teaming up with a top NFL quarterback. With numerous Big 12 weekly awards under his belt, Skattebo continues to make a significant impact on his team.
